{{Top|leg}}
'''Paaloc incense''' was a type of [[Incense/Legends|incense]] that was reserved for only the absolute highest-ranked members of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] caste system. Its scent was said to evoke memories of [[Yuuzhan'tar]], the Yuuzhan Vong's ancestral homeworld.<ref name="The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref> Lord [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] burned the incense within his [[Shimrra's Citadel|citadel]].

Because of its rarity, paaloc was outlawed amongst the lower castes; the penalty of execution awaited any Yuuzhan Vong of insufficient status caught possessing the substance.

